@5006 = ~Eddard~
@5007 = ~When asked about his past, EDDARD says you already met his family: Skie and their parents, Entar and Brilla. He was trained to become a responsible man, ready for all kinds of quests and challenges. His father hired the best swordsmen to teach him how to fight, while his mother's friend taught him the basics of magic. 
Even though he was taught to be all these things—a leader, a scholar, a fighter, a diplomat —Eddard also wanted to spend time with his sister, Skie. But their relationship wasn't easy. Eddard's education was focused on leadership, while Skie was expected to be "the good daughter", which clearly affected their bond.~
