@5037 = ~"Eight Cursed Gems" by Homleen Fallhood~
@5038 = ~This horror romance was written by Homleen Fallhood, a well-known and praised writer. It tells the story of eight friends, all hiding their secrets from each other. Every one of these secrets links them to the death of an elderly lady who used to live in an old cottage, just twenty minutes from the town of Braghlinn. Will revealing their secrets save them...? Or will it doom them and those they care about the most?
  
