@5039 = ~Broken Handband~
@5040 = ~This is a memento Eddard Silvershield took from his home and the only thing the slavers didn't take away from him. Even though it's broken, it still reminds its owner of his home and family.

When you ask Eddard if he'd like to repair it, he says it's not necessary. He rarely used to wear it, but took it with him because he felt better having part of his old life with him. This small item never lets him forget where he comes from.
  
STATISTICS:

Charge abilities:
- May cast Remove Fear once per day: 
The caster instills courage in the spell's recipients, raising their morale to its highest. The recipients' morale will gradually reset to normal as the duration runs out. If the recipients are affected by magical fear, this is negated. This version of the spell is centered on the handband's owner, Eddard.

