@5041 = ~Talk to Master Barkshield~
@5042 = ~Master Barkshield~
@5043 = ~This is the puppy Eddard Silvershield saved in Saradush. He took the dog with him as he was starving on the streets, and his mother was already gone. Eddard named him Master Barkshield. 

The dog is excellent at doing what the handband he destroyed used to do: making all the fear go away. However, he weighs a little more than the broken handband.

Eddard treats this dog as a very good friend.
  
